Package zti.zti_project.model

Class Reservation

java.lang.Object
zti.zti_project.model.Reservation
@Entity public class Reservation extends Object
A class representing the reservation PostreSQL entity in the system. It contains fields with information about the reservation such as: reservationId, repertoire, seat, user, ticket type, film date and film type.
